Prefix iteration is a small helper for server startup checks.  It takes a
snapshot under the lock and yields afterwards, avoiding a long-held lock around
caller code that merely consumes strings.

<<store methods>>=
def iter_prefixes(self) -> Iterator[str]:
    """Yield the URL prefix of every registered question."""

    with self._lock:
        data = self._data()

    for meta in data["questions"].values():
        yield meta["url_prefix"]
