For word-cloud answers, the aggregation test pins the contract every
renderer relies on: the [[frequencies]] entry is a list of two-element
[[[word, count]]] pairs sorted by descending count, with the two scalar
stats matching the totals derived from that list.  The store test
deliberately stays at the shape level --- the detailed filter behaviour
already has its own tests on [[WordCloudQuestion.frequencies]] in
[[questions.nw]].

